{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was night, and we were so damn tired, so we were walking back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said-- he said to me-- he says, 'You know what, Matthew?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's go into the straw,' he says, 'and hide in the straw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tomorrow, the Russians are going to be here, and we are going to be liberated.' I says, 'What happens if the Hungarians or the Germans capture you?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know you are going to be shot on the place.' He says, 'Don't be afraid.'",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what had happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went, and I-- whenever it was an alarm-- 4 o'clock in the morning, it was our alarm, the Russians starting to push.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an alarm, the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed-- put myself on the line with the other ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went here, there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "German soldiers, they went with the-- with the bayonets and their guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started into the straw, and they were hollering.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, 'Don't-- don't shoot!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't shoot!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are here.' They took out about 25 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They killed them on the place there, with my landlady's brother, together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Finally, they took us so long, the Hungarians-- they took us so long, now, until they took us to a place by the Austrian border, Austrian-Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was in Hungary, that was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There, Christmas Day, they gave us over to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't have what to do no more with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Their country was already invaded from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't have where to take us no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, they surrendered us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave it-- gave us over to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, here, start the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you know what to expect?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you know what the Germans were doing to the Jews?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
